Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:49.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this snow is so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:54.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially on days that HQ orders us to do thorough patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:55.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:02:00.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you haven't given up on Jacott-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:10.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Although you looked everywhere,\Nas long as you haven't found her, there's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:20.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You remind me a bit of Rio-senpai, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,About 400 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even her clothes are frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, take off her coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:05.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She can use mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.08,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,To actually restore this facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:45.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's what I call the greatest girl-genius\Nin the history of academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory will be ours with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:52.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Kannagi Noel-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They found her during their patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Roman soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like her left leg is fractured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all her fingers are dark-red.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's frostbite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't treat it properly, she could lose her fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Helvetian witch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Looks like she's finally stabilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Her fingers are okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}What about Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}She said she'll stay a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}But, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:07.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}The way she focuses on her is as if\Nshe's working on the Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:20.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be a scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't expect this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would've imagined finding a Roman soldier{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time seeing a Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone just calls them the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:42.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought they'd be more like a demon or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Romans probably think the same way about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I've seen her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:55.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to think the Romans are just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata! You{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kana-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,it's almost time for the evening call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:13.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace talks are still going poorly, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to report her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:24.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, she'll be taken to the\Ncentral government and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:33.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She infiltrated enemy territory during this unstable period.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:34.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd be ready for torture{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:43.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll decide how to deal with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:48.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give me time, Kureha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:11.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,When you brought her here, did anyone see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. We were too busy with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Helvetian soldier!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.66,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:50.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is this?! Am I a hostage of the Helvetians now?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't speak Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, you took me host{\fscx300}-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that scream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ground Forces of the Roman Empire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First Tank Division,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:26.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thirteenth Tank Batallion,\NCompany B, Sergeant Aisha Ardora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ID number, 1031021.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:32.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:36.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Army of the Roman Empire, Sergeant Aisha Ardora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ID number, 1031021.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Did you get anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem to understand any Helvetian.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:10:00.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We only got her ID number and her name, Aisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:06.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann,\Nthe commanding officer of this Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:13.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you have big boobs. That's just my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:17.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I fondled them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I feel you up as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So she truly doesn't understand Helvetian, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:33.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, this is troubling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't interrogate her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to find someone who can speak Roman right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:41.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:48.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we can properly interrogate her and file an\Nofficial report, we'll keep her under our unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... I thought of placing a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me, whatever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:03.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-chan, welcome to the Timekeeping Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Timekeeping Fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Timekeeping Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:12.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I actually made it here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandmother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "ah"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Is it too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:01.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You need stamina to escape, so I'm going to eat now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she said it was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:12.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata is her usual self, but Noel getting attached to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:16.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be her way to atone for her sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:23.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, have you ever seen a fossilized angel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Engel"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:32.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh right, you don't understand anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:35.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have learned Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:39.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right, if we could communicate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Working hard, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Oh, Yumina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have enough hands to clear the snow at the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:50.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That means they won't be kids forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:05.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,People grow day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.26,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Kanata-san's trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Rio would say she still had a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:13.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to Treize for supplies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:20.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff happened, so I came back empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speaking of the Fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a bad rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your trumpet is great!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:40.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't think there were still trumpets like these.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:44.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Rio-senpai would do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A great trumpet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To get to see something like this{\fscx300}-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that song you just played!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! This is so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya-san's note resounds in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And it resounds in Rio-senpai too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:28.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And the same song resounds\Nnot just in Helvetia, but Rome as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Notes do resound, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Be it Rome or Helvetia, they're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:51.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,First-aid treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Danke"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, thanks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "danke"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It means, "thank you".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So somebody saw us after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:22.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This town never experienced the brunt of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:25.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but almost all the residents, in one way or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:30.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,have lost someone they knew,\Nincluding parents, siblings, or relatives in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They're usually calm, but when things happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:38.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikhail, the one who owns that liquor store,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,remember him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:45.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to his place yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:50.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Helvetian Army is mobilizing on a large scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're heading this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:59.22,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If it has anything to do with that Roman soldier here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we need to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:12.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san, do you know anyone who understands Roman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,More than just know, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Yumina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I serve the Helvetian Orthodox Church.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May luck be with you always.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, you're one of the heretics!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:38.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is only one God. Such a greeting is blasphemy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a light greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need that, just ask her already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:55.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't talk, everyone here\Nwill wind up with extra work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you feel the slightest bit of gratitude,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you should speak the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:14.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't talk about my mission,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:19.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm here to see the fossilized angel\Nthat's supposedly in this town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's here to see the fossil of the angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fossil of the angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:26.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:34.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My grandmother once was in this guard fortress.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:38.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"My grandmother was a soldier of the Timekeeping Fortress."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was taken as a POW on the Eastern Front.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}She met my grandfather there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:45.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"She was captured and held prisoner on the\NEastern Front, and met my grandfather."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}When I was a child, she would often tell me about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"I was raised listening to her stories."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to see it, no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:57.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The angel my grandmother had seen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:02.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Angel of the Apocalypse that\Nbrought retribution unto the world long ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the wrong teaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.81,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who destroyed the world was a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:11.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us exactly what she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:17.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to see the\NAngel of Apocalypse that destroyed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.45,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The marching call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:33.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Royal Guard Platoon, 9th Independent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The 9th?! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Hopkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:43.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,They called him the "Knight of Vingt".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:49.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He activated a weapon from the old era\Nand obliterated three towns overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.49,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:03.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it seems you no longer have time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:07.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to decide now or you'll be in deep trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand her over or{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:10.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to think about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Helvetian Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost the bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It means you didn't make it, did you Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:25.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai said she didn't want anyone else to suffer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she'll do what she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she left, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:45.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,As the commanding officer of\NPlatoon 1121, these are my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This order will be based on my own judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:54.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take full responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Captain of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Filicia Heidemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:15.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A Roman scout was captured in Treize a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:21.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, there was an accident during the\Ninterrogation process, so we couldn't confirm anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:28.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidently, I received an eye-witness report\Nstating there was a Roman soldier here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Negative, Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:42.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,From now, the 1121st Fortress will be under the\Ncommand of the 9th Independent Mobile Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make loud noises!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:21:00.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisha-san told me about the legend of the Fire Maidens just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,According to her{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:06.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Search thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Found anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:09.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Break down the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.04,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Should be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal the exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:30.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she said she hasn't heard your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:31.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her name is Noel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:37.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel Kannagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:38.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:42.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who released the Invisible Reaper{\fscx300}-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The Invisible Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Was that a rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:58.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:17.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,1121st Platoon speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:25.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A large battalion of the Roman Army\Nappeared on the border of Seize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:19.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next episode: Echo in the Blue Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:18.20,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The radiance of this sky will carry to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:28.50,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The melody you dreamed of is like serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:33.51,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}For your hands the dream is still far away, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:38.51,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}remember the voice so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:51.19,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}when someone sang the chord of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:01:00.66,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The sound of the skies echoes high over all sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:11.30,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Everything reflected in your eyes is the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:20.64,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Not even the shedding of of tears can stop you here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.64,0:01:33.19,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}We're playing tomorrow in the light that rains without end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:50.97,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Resonate the feelings of love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:54.06,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's perform the important things
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:12.07,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I cried when I was happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:18.00,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I laughed when I was hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:27.34,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}But, they're all proof that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:31.47,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's walk slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.30,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:37.43,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Tell me what you truly want
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:38.68,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}You're just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:44.86,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even if love and friendship change over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.86,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1\3c&H5ECC69&}I know, You know little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:50.32,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I want them to echo forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:50.86,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1\3c&H5ECC69&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:56.62,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Speaking endless words touched by love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:24:02.75,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}This is our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:07.38,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I can hear our harmony
